sentences: In 1988 Nordvargr became part of the influential black industrial combo Maschinenzimmer 412 (later Mz.412).
The first album, Malfeitor, was released in 1989 on the Cold Meat Industry label.
In 2009 Nordvargr collaborated with Tim Bertilsson to produce the new project titled All Hail
